\"hkgmoji\" /> #41116<br />\n十五天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#57952<br />\n揾嚟搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #122718<br />\n立法會已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #28503<br />\nP.Dybala <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #57797<br />\nbbchu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #10894<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叧加不正常人類list:<br />\n蔣介石（翻生）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #2436<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部分已加入編號，另外編號後面嘅括號代表別名或者舊名，有啲可能已經改咗名，大家要提防list入面嘅人，希望有更多巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有寃枉，請大家多多指正，本人有錯即改！<br />\n<br />\n為免有支那人混淆名單誤導大家，名單紀錄只以我「1000歳（人瑞）」為準</span>"},{"pid":"b836e9ae66410b9669215e3608f8a4fae4c33d64","tid":457104,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國於1933年通過，並由希特勒簽署實施的動物保護法中，禁止不必要地傷害動物。比如在電影製作過程中出現對動物不人道的對待、將狗類用於狩獵用途、強迫灌食禽類和不人道的屠宰方式；另外，也禁止在不使用麻醉藥的情況下就剪短狗的尾巴和耳朵。德國政府更於1936年規定，魚類要先麻醉後才能宰殺，同時餐廳內宰殺龍蝦的速度必須越快越好。<br />\n<br />\n根據學者考證，希特勒是一位喜愛並關心動物處境的人，他反對為科學研究而殺害動物，認為賽馬是封建社會的殘留物，他本身更是徹底的素食主義者。1933年，曾被希特勒指定為接班人的納粹高層赫爾曼‧戈林（Hermann Goring），在一場宣佈「限制動物研究」的廣播中這麼說：「對德國人而言，動物不只是生物名詞中的動物，牠們過著自己的生活，並具有了解周遭環境的天賦。牠們能感覺痛苦、快樂，而且被證明是忠誠和依順的。」戈林亦曾威脅說：「我保證會將那些繼續把動物當作資產看待的人送到集中營。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8GAmFUGMcuA/SaxwEBLNgdI/AAAAAAAABsE/rTAeg0nM5CQ/s400/peta_hitler.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F_8GAmFUGMcuA%2FSaxwEBLNgdI%2FAAAAAAAABsE%2FrTAeg0nM5CQ%2Fs400%2Fpeta_hitler.jpg&h=4884ee89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d667b5c0e9bbf9fb8d1d41ff34b99abc01a1a247","tid":457104,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:18:40.000Z","msg":"左膠希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4d1e7615370be71b4101b5e896ec68135defb5","tid":457104,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左膠希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3042555d5c280f517ff8536cc5fb9043dc7437ba","tid":457104,"uid":116471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左膠希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.endalldisease.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hitlerdeer_thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.endalldisease.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2Fhitlerdeer_thumb.jpg&h=4fde0799&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be5df04ab5b537b217c08b55716dd2e7057ef1ca","tid":457104,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swiss_animal_protection_referendum,_1893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSwiss_animal_protection_referendum%2C_1893&d=DInV5Kwn2B2D1XXUe0Kj010Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a6a98461\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swiss_animal_protection_referendum,_1893</a>"},{"pid":"454aa63bbea7088d106cfb5d0ac69ccf9d9b8f13","tid":457104,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"對一隻豬，或者一頭牛，或者一隻羊而言，阿道夫&middot;希特勒是它們所能遇見的最大的善人。這個大屠殺者是如此虔誠的素食主義者，以至於看到電影中動物受傷的鏡頭都會流淚，用手遮住眼睛不看，懇求身邊的人「等鏡頭過去了再告訴他」。他常說，食肉者是偽善的「食屍者」，最終都不適合選入優等民族。一個早期採用的納粹宣傳方式是出售香菸，香菸盒內附一張照片：熱愛自然的元首若有所思地削著蘋果。事實上，德國素食團體對希特勒在權力舞台的崛起幫助如此之大，他甚至一度考慮要在其政黨綱領中加入不食肉這個內容，只是當他又想到此舉會損害到食物供給體系和他所做的戰爭努力，這才作罷。當他終於在1933 年執政，素食運動的領袖們齊聲歡呼，擁戴他為救世主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://read01.com/K04NEL.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FK04NEL.html&d=DInV5Kwn2B2D1XXUe0Kj010Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c7adc909\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/K04NEL.html</a>"}]}